
dpkg-changelog (1.8.147) unstable; urgency=optional

  * Made git branch handling better by checking what branch is being build.
  * Fix output path for control file in set-control script
  * Add version file with initial version number 1.6.137
  * Update .gitignore to clarify version entry and remove debian directory
  * Add initial configuration and man page files for dpkg-changelog
  * Changed License to GNU General Public License v3 to copyright file
  * Add debian/control file for package metadata and dependencies
  * Remove obsolete DEBIAN rule file to streamline package management
  * Modified app to handle versioning better, and moved location.

 -- Michael Schaecher <MichaelLeeSchaecher@gmail.com>  Sat, 19 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000

