dpkg-changelog (1.6.129) unstable; urgency=optional

  * * Refactor Makefile and scripts for improved package management: * Update PACKAGE and HOMEPAGE variables to be dynamic. * Add DESCRIPTION and LONG_DESCRIPTION variables for better documentation. * Introduce gen-chsums script for generating md5sums. * Enhance mkdeb script to check for existing deb files and handle force option. * Modify set-control script to use new description variables. * Remove obsolete sum script.

